    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "1 Thessalonians",
        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 4,
        "summary": "The Saints are told to be holy, sanctify themselves, and love one another\u2014The Lord will come, and the dead will rise.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "Furthermore then we beseech you, brethren, and exhort you by the Lord Jesus, that as ye have received of us how ye ought to walk and to please God, so ye would abound more and more.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Philip. 4:9.",
                        "start": 93,
                        "end": 101
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Walking with God.",
                        "start": 124,
                        "end": 128
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Col. 1:10.",
                        "start": 136,
                        "end": 142
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Thes. 3:12.",
                        "start": 160,
                        "end": 166
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 54,
                        "end": 57
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 148,
                        "end": 150
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For ye know what commandments we gave you by the Lord Jesus.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 1:38.",
                        "start": 30,
                        "end": 32
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For this is the will of God, even your sanctification, that ye should abstain from fornication:",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Heb. 12:14.",
                        "start": 39,
                        "end": 53
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Abstain.",
                        "start": 70,
                        "end": 77
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0immorality. TG\u00a0Chastity; Fornication; Sexual Immorality; Whore.",
                        "start": 83,
                        "end": 94
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 29,
                        "end": 33
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "That every one of you should know how to possess his vessel in sanctification and honour;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Body, Sanctity of.",
                        "start": 53,
                        "end": 59
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Sanctification.",
                        "start": 63,
                        "end": 77
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Not in the lust of concupiscence, even as the Gentiles which know not God:",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0passion of lust. TG\u00a0Lust; Marriage, Husbands.",
                        "start": 11,
                        "end": 32
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Eph. 4:17 (17, 19).",
                        "start": 46,
                        "end": 54
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Eph. 2:12 (11\u201312).",
                        "start": 61,
                        "end": 69
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "That no man go beyond and defraud his brother in any matter: because that the Lord is the avenger of all such, as we also have forewarned you and testified.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0take advantage of, wrong.",
                        "start": 12,
                        "end": 33
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Thes. 1:8.",
                        "start": 90,
                        "end": 97
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 8,
                        "end": 11
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 49,
                        "end": 52
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 83,
                        "end": 85
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For God hath not called us unto uncleanness, but unto holiness.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Uncleanness.",
                        "start": 32,
                        "end": 43
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "He therefore that despiseth, despiseth not man, but God, who hath also given unto us his holy Spirit.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0rejects, sets aside, violates.",
                        "start": 18,
                        "end": 27
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Luke 10:16.",
                        "start": 29,
                        "end": 38
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Cor. 2:10; 1\u00a0Jn. 3:24.",
                        "start": 89,
                        "end": 100
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "But as touching brotherly love ye need not that I write unto you: for ye yourselves are taught of God to love one another.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Brotherhood and Sisterhood.",
                        "start": 16,
                        "end": 30
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "John 6:45; 1\u00a0Jn. 2:27 (20, 27).",
                        "start": 88,
                        "end": 94
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Love.",
                        "start": 105,
                        "end": 109
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And indeed ye do it toward all the brethren which are in all Macedonia: but we beseech you, brethren, that ye increase more and more;",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And that ye study to be quiet, and to do your own business, and to work with your own hands, as we commanded you;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0strive, endeavor earnestly.",
                        "start": 12,
                        "end": 17
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Industry; Labor; Skill; Work, Value of.",
                        "start": 67,
                        "end": 71
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Prov. 31:13.",
                        "start": 86,
                        "end": 91
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "That ye may walk honestly toward them that are without, and that ye may have lack of nothing.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Dependability; Honesty.",
                        "start": 17,
                        "end": 25
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 60,
                        "end": 64
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "But I would not have you to be ignorant, brethren, concerning them which are asleep, that ye sorrow not, even as others which have no hope.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Despair; Mourning; Sorrow.",
                        "start": 93,
                        "end": 99
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Eph. 2:12.",
                        "start": 134,
                        "end": 138
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For if we believe that Jesus died and rose again, even so them also which sleep in Jesus will God bring with him.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Zech. 14:5.",
                        "start": 74,
                        "end": 79
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For this we say unto you by the word of the Lord, that we which are alive and remain unto the coming of the Lord shall not prevent them which are asleep.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "JST\u00a01\u00a0Thes. 4:15 \u2026 that they who are alive at the coming of the Lord, shall not prevent them who remain unto the coming of the Lord, who are asleep.",
                        "start": 50,
                        "end": 54
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Thes. 2:2 (1\u20133).",
                        "start": 55,
                        "end": 57
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0precede, make progress over.",
                        "start": 123,
                        "end": 130
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 74,
                        "end": 77
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For the Lord himself shall descend from heaven with a shout, with the voice of the archangel, and with the trump of God: and the dead in Christ shall rise first:",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Second Coming.",
                        "start": 27,
                        "end": 34
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0a cry of command, a cheer.",
                        "start": 52,
                        "end": 59
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Adam.",
                        "start": 83,
                        "end": 92
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Matt. 24:31.",
                        "start": 107,
                        "end": 112
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Resurrection.",
                        "start": 150,
                        "end": 154
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Then we which are alive and remain shall be caught up together with them in the clouds, to meet the Lord in the air: and so shall we ever be with the Lord.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "JST\u00a01\u00a0Thes. 4:17 Then they who are alive, shall be caught up together into the clouds with them who remain, to meet the Lord in the air; and so shall we be ever with the Lord.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 4
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Cor. 15:51; D&C 88:96 (96\u201397); 101:31; 109:75.",
                        "start": 44,
                        "end": 53
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Jude 1:14 (14\u201316).",
                        "start": 100,
                        "end": 104
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Moro. 10:34.",
                        "start": 112,
                        "end": 115
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Immortality.",
                        "start": 133,
                        "end": 137
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "John 14:3; Rev. 22:4 (3\u20135).",
                        "start": 150,
                        "end": 154
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 24,
                        "end": 27
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Wherefore comfort one another with these words.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            }
        ]
    }
}